WEBVTT

00:00.209 --> 00:01.836
[Bosch]
Previously on Bosch: Legacy.

00:01.919 --> 00:03.003
[tires screech]

00:03.087 --> 00:04.046
Gun, gun, gun!

00:05.881 --> 00:08.676
Rose and Associates have begun
the process of filing a civil suit

00:08.759 --> 00:12.012
against the city of Los Angeles
and the LAPD

00:12.096 --> 00:14.724
on behalf of Nicole's son, Kalon.

00:14.807 --> 00:18.144
I was able to identify the SIS Lieutenant.
Spencer Cosgrove.

00:18.227 --> 00:21.147
Chandler will distort the truth.
She'll inflame public opinion.

00:21.230 --> 00:22.523
Well, it won't be hard.

00:22.606 --> 00:24.942
The whole department
will be under siege.

00:25.025 --> 00:26.485
We need to stick together on this.

00:26.569 --> 00:29.947
[Golliher] Dr. Basu had five stab wounds,
all to vital blood vessels.

00:30.030 --> 00:31.532
The killer knew what he was doing.

00:31.615 --> 00:35.453
I'd wager the assailant has
some military or medical background.

00:35.536 --> 00:36.370
Can you describe him?

00:36.454 --> 00:37.997
He was wearing a mask.

00:38.080 --> 00:40.708
One of those
Mexican wrestling masks.

00:40.791 --> 00:43.294
We're not detectives
and we sure as shit aren't social workers.

00:43.377 --> 00:44.962
Case belongs to Sex Crimes now.

00:45.129 --> 00:46.589
What happened with that Thai Town call?

00:46.672 --> 00:48.215
Attempted rape. Suspect fled.

00:48.299 --> 00:49.216
She get a good look at him?

00:49.300 --> 00:50.718
Wearing a luchador mask.

00:50.801 --> 00:52.219
Red and black?

00:52.303 --> 00:54.638
[Bosch]
Any update on Vance's probate?

00:54.722 --> 00:57.516
It's still uncontested.
We need to confirm Vance's heir.

00:57.600 --> 01:01.228
If it stays uncontested, all shares
and interest will pass to the board.

01:01.312 --> 01:04.190
My client was the biological father
of Dominick Santanello.

01:04.273 --> 01:05.107
Your grandfather.

01:05.191 --> 01:07.818
You should know
his estate goes to his heirs.

01:07.902 --> 01:08.736
You and your son.

01:09.862 --> 01:12.448
If DNA confirms bloodlines,
which it will.

01:12.531 --> 01:13.783
So how much?

01:13.866 --> 01:14.867
Billions.

01:16.035 --> 01:17.703
Better guard those with your life.

01:17.787 --> 01:19.705
Oh, I'm gonna take them straight there.

01:19.789 --> 01:22.374
BioRight Testing's good, reliable.

01:22.458 --> 01:23.501
Better be.

01:23.584 --> 01:25.795
We need to do something
about this DNA situation.

01:25.878 --> 01:28.756
We need to strangle
the baby in the crib, so to speak.

01:31.342 --> 01:34.303
Mr. Creighton, I understand
you have work for me.

01:34.386 --> 01:35.846
Indeed, I do.

01:43.938 --> 01:46.273
[suspenseful music playing]

02:22.142 --> 02:22.977
